<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">There are so many bumbclot references in this book I almost found myself using the term. I looked it up on Urban Dictionary:<br/><br/>bumbaclot <br/>A cloth or rag u<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">There are so many bumbclot references in this book I almost found myself using the term. I looked it up on Urban Dictionary:<br /><br />bumbaclot <br />A cloth or rag used to wipe ones anal region. However, most Jamaicans use it as a substitute for the word f*ck to express anger or surprise.<br />Bumbaclot! Dem tek mi rolex and mi new links!!<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
