<span id="freeTextContainer2404391341290576366"><b>Reader Response A:</b> Hey, waiter! What the hell gives, mac? There&apos;s a goddamned experimental novel in my crime novel! You expect me to read this shit?<br/><br/><b>Reader Response B:</b> <i>S&apos;il vous plaît, monsieur?</i> Terribly sorry to be a bother, but there must have been some confusion with my order. You see, there seems to be a <i>crime</i> novel in my experimental novel. I&apos;m afraid I don&apos;t have quite the palate for such things.<br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText2404391341290576366" style="display:none"><b>Reader Response A:</b> Hey, waiter! What the hell gives, mac? There's a goddamned experimental novel in my crime novel! You expect me to read this shit?<br /><br /><b>Reader Response B:</b> <i>S'il vous plaît, monsieur?</i> Terribly sorry to be a bother, but there must have been some confusion with my order. You see, there seems to be a <i>crime</i> novel in my experimental novel. I'm afraid I don't have quite the palate for such things.<br /><br /></span>
