<li class='cover' id='bookCover_22237161'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/22237161-the-sellout"><img alt="The Sellout" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1403430899l/22237161._SX98_.jpg" />
